委外建造第三、第四福特級航母</blockquote><br />\n<blockquote>   &nbsp;The first-of-class USS&nbsp;Gerald R. Ford&nbsp;(CVN-78),&nbsp;commissioned&nbsp;in July 2017, is already the U.S. Navy&rsquo;s most expensive warship in its history, with total cost amounting to almost $13 billion. The per-unit cost of<span style=\"color: red;\"> the remaining ships of the class is estimated at around $10 billion</span>.&nbsp;</blockquote><br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n台灣記者咩事"},{"pid":"555bcd7b15482a9215420691a4536763dd7bf6b7","tid":891780,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T23:49:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>  Problems with the elevators add to questions about the Navy&rsquo;s plan to bundle the third and fourth carriers in the <span style=\"color: red;\">$58 billion Ford class</span> into one contract.&nbsp; </blockquote><br />\n58B係包埋第一至第四航母造價喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f54e2ab681abcb755d3a5c2d737b45d709772ef","tid":891780,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T00:04:43.000Z","msg":"點解仲平過港珠澳大橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26d2b95d451d29370133b39a3be234cbb68089b5","tid":891780,"uid":78304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T00:45:24.000Z","msg":"香港人用晒D儲備買武器, 勞役中國人都仲得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38c5d6c285b9d2881f9a884b1cb6e6cfe01c74d1","tid":891780,"uid":33874,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T00:53:44.000Z","msg":"是旦啦<br />\n佢有需要，一個月起十隻出嚟都仲得<br />\n會因為你條梯郁唔到"},{"pid":"832bc5ecd7ee30fac2f99696e0ba546469b54e17","tid":891780,"uid":10064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T01:32:20.000Z","msg":"不能同不急係有分別既<br />\n人地都唔急你急咩？"},{"pid":"ab68d7636a9b8df9622d5592e1c405c6b21d2c6